{"type": "article", "id": 28846, "title": "打印机", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-29T06:59:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703123234m79eCKFZ4futPwMQ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>作为常用的办公设备，打印机千篇一律的造型是不是已经让你感到乏味，好像进入了一间没有美感的打印室？今天我们要介绍的 <a href=\"http://www.ludwigrensch.com/paper-a-printer-you-actually-want\">Paper</a> 是德国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.ludwigrensch.com/\">Ludwig Rensch</a> 的作品，他的初衷是打造一款功能齐全而且不影响室内环境的打印机。Rensch 用按钮和信号灯替代了常见的触摸式显示屏，即使需要手动操作也很容易上手。它同时具有打印、扫描和复印三种功能，通过专门的应用和网页传输资料。橙色机身更是为沉闷的办公环境注入了一股温暖活泼的感觉。它目前还是一款概念产品，尚未投入生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123232i92wkvRXY5rcBpt6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123232hrjsQykGVBIvgnHb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123233nhE1TOs2lor65baU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123233Kp45JfBN6GQExmRZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}